Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth has a skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:07.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,and that skin is plagued \Nby many different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,One of those plagues is humanity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:12.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We are that which cures the \NEarth of its plagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:14.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Council of the Seven Virtues.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:17.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Born from the plague, but not of the plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:20.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Number Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:23.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,A heretic that can perceive the flags,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:27.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,and control fate with his own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,We must assess this heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:34.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a true messenger of the Sacraments,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,or will he bring harm to this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:38.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This will be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:42.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,Man is a rope—a rope over an abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:44.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,A dangerous across, a dangerous on-the-way,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:48.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,a dangerous looking-back, \Na dangerous shuddering and stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,And I think he
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Zero,0000,0000,0000,,represents the rope we see before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:02.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Daimyouzamurai Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:04.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you all.
