Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:41.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{titles}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,Just ask me if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:47.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any boy trouble, \NI'll be glad to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:51.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in the opposite sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:54.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Dude,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:56.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You want to get some crêpes on the way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:00.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I gain weight every time I eat too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:02.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,My boobs, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,The world's so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:07.86,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,A person with the same power as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:09.40,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:13.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You just sighed looking at someone. \NWho was it, Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,My name was on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:17.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the forest with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:20.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I get to go on the ocean trip with Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:21.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.51,Ocean_03:24,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean Field Trip
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.51,Forest_03:24,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Forest Field Trip
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.51,hatate_souta_left_03:24,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.51,hatate_souta_right_03:24,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my name on both lists?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:31.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me to clear that up for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:32.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:33.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.58,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, Hatate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:41.59,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,We normally would have \Nyou go on the ocean trip
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.79,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,since your swimming grades are bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.54,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,but Eiyuuzaki-kun threatened me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.09,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, asked me to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:49.30,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,So I put you on the ocean trip \Nduring the first half of the trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.96,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,and the forest trip for the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:54.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't really sound like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.33,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,You get to see the ocean and the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:59.89,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,and you get to have fun with \Neveryone from Quest Dorm easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:00.61,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:03.26,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, how about going on a date with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.01,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,while you're at it--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a good time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:11.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, everyone in Quest Dorm gets \Nto spend half their time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun, Sou-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:16.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,if you ever get lonely, just come to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:22.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling there was just a \N"this is going to be trouble" flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:28.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Non non!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Non non!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The beach, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Now we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:57.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,After hiking you've got \Nmake-up lessons, Akane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:59.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get you into \Nshape on those mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:05.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,You kind of feel bad for Akane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:07.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:09.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be lodging in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the ocean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,This is your first time seeing the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:21.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my country is surrounded by land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:23.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you should come in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good on my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:29.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You won't rust if you get in \Nthe water, will you, Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:33.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I have special waterproof coating,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:34.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,so I should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:39.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Souta, don't just stand there. Join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:44.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you can't swim though, Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You were great at track.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:49.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do any swimming at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:50.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know boy swimsuits
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,only have bottoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't mind now because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:09.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why'd you poke me in the eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I shouldn't have... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:15.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,They have boy swimsuits with a top now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:17.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Tee-hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:20.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you swim, Souta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you guys have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:30.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew you had such big boobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:38.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Girls with bigger boobs look \Ngood in kimonos, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:40.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She was wearing a uniform, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Go for a swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:50.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Barf, barf, barf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,That's gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:01.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Souta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not feel well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't handle getting \Ntoo close to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It all comes back to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,The Premium Ambriel, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:18.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,He saw all of the destruction and despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you had such a tough time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You must have had it rough, Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:43.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you learn to swim, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:45.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Like a grandma taking care of her grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:50.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri, watch after little \NNanami and little Megumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:52.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of little Souta, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:01.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:07.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as a giant puddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Barf, barf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making a mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:17.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Want to take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:23.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I think I'll do that, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:32.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:42.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't taste like anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:43.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I got some milk and put enough water into it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:48.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,until it looked like your \Naverage sports drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a popsicle for \N100 yen to go along with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You were trying to sell me things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:57.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:59.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I gave that to you because \NI thought you needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:02.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to buy anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:09.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:15.57,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She'll move the story to the next stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:17.74,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's a story flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:19.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:20.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the 100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:30.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You're here on a field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Daishikyougawa Kurumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:36.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Daishikyougawa (Bishop)?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not getting heat stroke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:45.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you always around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:47.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:49.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:52.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:55.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Please buy something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Kikuno-senpai and Rin-chan-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,keep whispering this chant every \Ntime they get close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make people get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We just told you the formulas \Nyou needed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:29.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrible with numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:32.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why you got assigned to the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,forest trip when your grades were so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:37.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun, were you able to swim again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:38.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You've been through so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:48.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you have to keep \Ngoing through all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:49.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a good girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,crying for little Souta over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:58.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love for you two to have a kid and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:11:01.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,show me a cute grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Nanami-chan and Megu-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:09.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,would make a cuter child!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:14.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure I can help there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:18.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, how old are you really, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,It's rude to worry about a woman's age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:26.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I'm kind of curious to know \Nif you've always looked so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:28.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:36.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:39.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,You shrink when you get older.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,No... No... No... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:45.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugi,0000,0000,0000,,A few decades and you'll look like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:53.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to reach the halfway point for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,both the forest trip and the ocean trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:58.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally get away from the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:01.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,So tomorrow, as a change of pace,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have the guy and girls
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:06.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,from the forest trip go to the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:08.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,and vice-versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:08.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,The beach is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:17.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it really feels like summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I've been had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:22.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun! It's the beach! The beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. It's the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:28.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Barf! Barf! Barf!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:38.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:45.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go and have fun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:48.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,all by myself without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:49.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:50.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You just left him there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:57.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel worse if you guys just sat here \Nworrying about me instead of having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:02.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:04.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,If Souta insists...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:12.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to go \Nswimming today, either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:13.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The water's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:20.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You must be working pretty hard every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't work hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:25.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,my parents in heaven won't be able to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:27.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:31.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have new products today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:33.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I can put these on your tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:38.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,My mom and dad always said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:43.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't depend on other \Npeople and remember that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:45.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get by on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:50.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong, Kurumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:56.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sea cucumber!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:00.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's so slimy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:04.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You're always with a \Ndifferent girl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:06.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:13.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Daishikyougawa Kurumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:18.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I sell popsicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:22.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you're Souta-kun's \Nfriend, then you're my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Let me buy all of your stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for getting everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What a flashy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:36.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she was born into a rich family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Rich... family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:41.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like selling popsicles?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:44.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:47.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying to make enough \Nto live and go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're working to \Nput yourself through school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:00.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Akane,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:04.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:06.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:17.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought about how \Nthere could be someone there
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,that could just buy all of \Nmy stuff just like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:23.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I belonged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:25.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you need to be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Struggling to be alive, to look \Nat becoming something more,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,that's something that only humans can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:36.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No one has a right to laugh \Nat someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:39.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:42.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that girl means a lot to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:46.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane's such a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Her name's Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I should apologize to \Nher next time I see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:54.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I should apologize to you and thank you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:16:01.23,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The story flag has progressed \Nto the next stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I'm having a hard time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:27.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I come here and remember \Nwhat my parents told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:31.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,"You shouldn't depend on other \Npeople and remember that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,you need to get by on your own," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:36.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't that bad to depend \Non others, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:46.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I couldn't tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:49.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,When I first gave you that drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:52.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I knew who you were, that's why I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:53.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You knew who I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:56.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,My parents were crew on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:02.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,the Premium Ambriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So you hated me because of that and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You should hate me instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:15.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,It was the duty of the staff to \Nmake sure everyone was safe, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:19.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,The TV and newspapers made \Nit all sound like your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So when you said you weren't \Ngoing to depend on anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:26.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,you wanted to carry that burden,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:29.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,that cross in the stead of your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:33.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's been so hard every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:37.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to give up on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:42.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:45.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the only one in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:49.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing I thought that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:52.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you won't forgive me for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:54.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,trying to seek help from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,There was no reason
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:04.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,for you to carry that cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:08.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You're really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:12.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:13.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The tide
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:18.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,came in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:27.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't brought you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:31.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame yourself so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:36.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,If I had a brother like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I would
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:41.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,have been a lot happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:43.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,If I had a nice sister like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure everything would be different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:48.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:51.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.15,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:56.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,If we're able to get out of here safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:59.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,would you promise we'll become
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:01.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,brother and sister in spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.87,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Death flags...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.57,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get rid of those...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:09.29,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell her no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:13.98,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... No, I don't know \Nwhy, but that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.13,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to tell her no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:19.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,let's become real brothers and sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:21.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,not something "in spirit."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.94,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the power of the story flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:35.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:39.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to be your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to worry about anything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:44.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,having a nice brother like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:49.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy with just you as my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.21,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they coming up like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:52.96,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:55.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me to Hatagaya Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:56.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:59.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,There's a middle school dorm there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we can do something \Nabout the tuition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:05.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,everyone there helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:13.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you might not want to go, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:17.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:20.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:33.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:38.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Mimori-san told me that it would be \Ngood to surprise people like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,so I gave it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:40.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Someone came to save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:47.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Or should we be saving her instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:51.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,beyond our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I've found Souta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:57.01,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:59.33,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried when I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.11,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,found out he was missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me to rescue you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:15.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay for me to go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:18.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have to introduce \Nyou to everyone, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:12.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:15.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:17.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:21.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of like friends of friends \Njust kind of sat down with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:24.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,and it's kind of awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:28.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I guess you'll have to \Nwatch the next episode to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:33.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we just had the "you did \Na good job on the preview" flag.
